<div class="container">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span3">
      <h3>Clocker Signup</h3>
      <form method="post" action="/account/register" class="form-condensed form-popdown-errors">
        <div class="control-group {{#errors.email}}error{{/errors.email}}">
          <div class="controls">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" value="{{attributes.email}}" autofocus />
            <span class="help-inline">{{errors.email}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="control-group {{#errors.password}}error{{/errors.password}}">
          <div class="controls">
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" />
            <span class="help-inline">{{errors.password}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="control-group {{#errors.password_confirmation}}error{{/errors.password_confirmation}}">
          <div class="controls">
            <input type="password" name="password_confirmation" placeholder="Confirm Password" />
            <span class="help-inline">{{errors.password_confirmation}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>
          <small class="muted">We won't email you unless you ask!</small>
        </p>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Create Account <i class="icon-ok"></i></button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="span8 offset1">
      <h3>Why should I use Clocker?</h3>
      <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span4">
          <h5><i class="icon-heart"></i> No nonsense features</h5>
          <p>
            Clocker was designed to be a useful, single purpose utility. There are no bloated features and no extra
            cruft making the application confusing to use. Simplicity is Beauty.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h5><i class="icon-calendar"></i> Easy Time Tracking</h5>
          <p>
            Clocker makes it dead simple to clock in when you start working on a project, and to then later come back to
            clock out for the day. No fuss, just a simple button click.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h5><i class="icon-print"></i> PDF Invoice Generation</h5>
          <p>
            When you're ready to send out an invoice for your most recent work entries Clocker can generate a beautiful
            PDF ready to be emailed off to your client. They're customizable too!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
